article.description: — Nick Dorn scored 19 points as Elon beat IUPUI 86-72 on Friday night.
article.headline: Dorn has 19, Elon takes down IUPUI 86-72
article.linkText: Dorn has 19, Elon takes down IUPUI 86-72
article.story: ROCK HILL, S.C. -- — Nick Dorn scored 19 points as Elon beat IUPUI 86-72 on Friday night. Dorn was 6 of 12 shooting, including 4 for 9 from 3-point range, and went 3 for 4 from the line for the Phoenix (2-2). TK Simpkins was 5 of 7 shooting and 7 of 9 from the free throw line to add 19 points. LA Pratt was 6 of 9 shooting (4 for 7 from 3-point range) to finish with 16 points. Jlynn Counter led the way for the Jaguars (2-2) with 20 points. John Egbuta added 10 points and nine rebounds for IUPUI. In addition, Bryce Monroe had 10 points and four assists. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
